---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout 
  title="Privacy Policy | The Birdie Report"
  description="Privacy policy for The Birdie Report website."
>
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-8">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mb-8">Last updated: March 16, 2026</p>
    
    <div class="prose prose-lg text-gray-700 space-y-6">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8">Information We Collect</h2>
      <p>
        We collect minimal information. If you subscribe to our newsletter, we collect your email address. We use standard web analytics to understand how visitors use our site (pages visited, time on site, etc.). We do not sell your personal information to anyone.
      </p>
      
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8">Cookies</h2>
      <p>
        Our site uses cookies for basic functionality and analytics. Third-party affiliate links (such as Amazon) may set their own cookies to track referrals. These cookies are governed by the respective company's privacy policies.
      </p>
      
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8">Affiliate Links</h2>
      <p>
        Our site contains affiliate links to products on third-party websites. When you click these links, you will be redirected to the retailer's site, which has its own privacy policy. We earn a commission on qualifying purchases at no extra cost to you. See our <a href="/affiliate-disclosure/" class="text-green-700 hover:text-green-800 underline">Affiliate Disclosure</a> for more details.
      </p>
      
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8">Third-Party Services</h2>
      <p>
        We may use third-party services for analytics, email delivery, and advertising. These services may collect information as described in their own privacy policies.
      </p>
      
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8">Your Rights</h2>
      <p>
        You may unsubscribe from our newsletter at any time using the link in any email. If you'd like your data removed, <a href="/contact/" class="text-green-700 hover:text-green-800 underline">contact us</a> and we'll take care of it.
      </p>
      
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8">Contact</h2>
      <p>
        Questions about this privacy policy? Reach out at <a href="/contact/" class="text-green-700 hover:text-green-800 underline">our contact page</a>.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
